                        android:text="Step 1:- Hereâ€™s a simple way of making this delicacy at home. Soak black gram (urad dal) in water for about an hour and rinse well. Then drain the water and grind urad dal, till it turns into a thick paste. Do not add too much of water, just sprinkle a little bit water to achieve a balanced consistency of batter."
